Sentencas: Viscosity of a specific Ba-B-Si-Al-O glass used for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell was measured using indentation creep tests.
Titulo: Viscosity of Ba-B-Si-Al-O glass measured by indentation creep test at operating temperature of IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Responses of shear strain to corresponding shear stress at the operating temperature of solid oxide fuel cell were analyzed, and the results revealed that the glass system possesses Newtonian flow behavior at 600-630 degrees C.
Titulo: Viscosity of Ba-B-Si-Al-O glass measured by indentation creep test at operating temperature of IT-SOFC

Sentencas: In addition, the stress exponent and the activation energy for viscous flow at different temperatures and stresses were also determined.
Titulo: Viscosity of Ba-B-Si-Al-O glass measured by indentation creep test at operating temperature of IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Finally, the absolute-rate theory was adopted to describe the viscous flow for the glass.
Titulo: Viscosity of Ba-B-Si-Al-O glass measured by indentation creep test at operating temperature of IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The results were compared with other glass systems.
Titulo: Viscosity of Ba-B-Si-Al-O glass measured by indentation creep test at operating temperature of IT-SOFC
